Junction tables of join tables are only used for many to many relations, so in order to fit your current data model to sequelize you will have to do:

``` js
Hole.hasMany(TrackingGroup, {foreignKey: 'hole_id', joinTableName:'holes_tracking_groups', underscored: true}); 
